title: #237 Over and Out
description:
It's another hot Tuesdays as Joe gets into dealing with a jerk at the Big East Tournament with Stavros Halkias and his nightmare trip in the NYC snowstorm while Mark takes in a Hornets game in Charlotte and travels to L.A. to perform on Conan! Check it out!
